            <description><![CDATA[“留学哈工大”品牌系列学生活动——【Hi-Talk】咖啡角第二十四期活动预告]]></description>
            <link>https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/15/120839</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="true">https://today.hit.edu.cn/article/2025/04/15/120839</guid>
            <pubDate>Tue, 15 Apr 2025 06:42:12 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded>&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Let&apos;s speak up! Hi-Talk咖啡角来啦~&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;加入咖啡角，与来自世界各地的中外学生建立联系，探索丰富多彩的文化盛宴！&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Join the Coffee Corner program to build friendships between Chinese students and international students and to explore different cultures!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;主讲人介绍：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;大家好，我是Gnagna，本周四我将和大家分享塞内加尔的文化与历史。塞内加尔有着迷人的艺术和建筑遗产值得探索。博物馆、美术馆和历史遗迹能让人们得以了解这个国家的文化与历史，而各类节日和文化活动则让游客和当地居民能够尽情欣赏塞内加尔的艺术珍品、体验舞蹈以及感受当地传统。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Hi everyone, I’m Gnagna and this Thursday I’m gonna share with you about culture and history in Senegal with fascinating and architectural heritage to discover. Museums, art galleries and historical sites offer a glimpse into the country’s culture and history, while festivals and cultural events allow visitors and residents to enjoy Senegalese museums, dance, and local traditions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; data-entity-type=&quot;file&quot; data-entity-uuid=&quot;7eb90c8b-b0e3-4f2b-b238-f26b186a92e2&quot; src=&quot;/sites/today1.prod1.dpweb1.hit.edu.cn/files/inline-images/2025/04/15/1_1.jpg&quot; class=&quot;align-center&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;本周四晚&lt;/span&gt;18:30，暖廊骑楼五楼学业工作室，我们不见不散！&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;This Thursday evening at 18:30, Skywalk, 5th Floor, Qi Lou Academic Studio, Let&apos;s meet again!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; data-entity-type=&quot;file&quot; data-entity-uuid=&quot;a65f9867-3b9b-48cc-866b-369a911d0b88&quot; src=&quot;/sites/today1.prod1.dpweb1.hit.edu.cn/files/inline-images/2025/04/15/2.jpg&quot; class=&quot;align-center&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;活动地点指示图：&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;活动地点为暖廊骑楼五楼学业工作室，骑楼位于A11公寓与A12公寓之间。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;Please follow the directions below：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;The event will be held at Skywalk , 5th Floor, Qi Lou Academic Studio. Qi Lou is located between A11 Apartment and A12 Apartment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; data-entity-type=&quot;file&quot; data-entity-uuid=&quot;c703bd08-ef71-4196-b7d2-53834958da8f&quot; src=&quot;/sites/today1.prod1.dpweb1.hit.edu.cn/files/inline-images/2025/04/15/3_1.jpg&quot; class=&quot;align-center&quot;&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent:21.0pt; text-align:justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:white&quot;&gt;本期活动主题：塞内加尔文化分享&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

